  "detailed_description": "<h1>Games From Quebec 2024</h1><p><strong>Build A City Block</strong> 🏙 will be featured in the <strong><u>2024 Quebec Games Celebration</u></strong> 🎉.<br>Check it out for a major discount.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/fab152fdf5b37eb218ca21507118009d.avif?t=1720811359\" width=640 height=1040 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong><u>Build A City Block </u></strong>is a dynamic <u>puzzle game</u> where you raise beautiful <u>city landscapes</u> by filling <u>districts </u>with blocks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/d9499a2102b44a551f7e67effd02c5f4.avif?t=1720811359\" width=640 height=206 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/f887adc9fa1b815d63f299b19fe0b9ae.avif?t=1720811359\" width=128 height=84 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/ad3b929b42522a314e3909776658a80a.avif?t=1720811359\" width=128 height=84 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/ef86af561aef3a0edcb2e05747961eff.avif?t=1720811359\" width=128 height=84 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/92bf58d33a5debfb717e4339bd1a2165.avif?t=1720811359\" width=84 height=84 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/b3bb6049fe00a3e0ba1d21ad5b927124.avif?t=1720811359\" width=128 height=84 /></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/34b2ea3310cd9b1978343c42c163a9ca.webp?t=1720811359\" width=192 height=35 /></span><br>All <strong>Tetris fans </strong>will enjoy this game, which is offering a fresh twist to the popular classic.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/1407db527215b0b35b32741281d89570.poster.avif?t=1720811359\" width=432 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/1407db527215b0b35b32741281d89570.webm?t=1720811359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/1407db527215b0b35b32741281d89570.mp4?t=1720811359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Instead or dropping blocks, you place them on a <u>top-down grid</u>. You will find the same <i>transcending</i> feeling as in the old Tetris.<br><br>And don't worry, thankfully it is <u>less stressful</u> than the original Tetris. You have <strong>more time</strong> to figure out the best move. Time extenders can even be purchased with coins. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/30946091de3e38cc304adfcde5d24463.webp?t=1720811359\" width=307 height=36 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/64394f9bbed334e952e4a99b943b6645.avif?t=1720811359\" width=600 height=132 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/6b65eecef8b41d33b71d0903b7e60354.avif?t=1720811359\" width=600 height=132 /></span><br>Each cities have its <u>unique map</u> and <u>challenges</u>.<br>Changing the grid layout produces a different experience which required a different strategy.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/958437e21af343290ff715f74fc74c5e.webp?t=1720811359\" width=425 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/5583cada08db85909cc353e4700b99b7.avif?t=1720811359\" width=580 height=160 /></span><br>Each cities have their own <u>unique landmarks</u>. <br>You first have to unlock individual <u>blue-prints</u>. Then, <u>stars </u>need to be collected by filling blocks.<br>Will you be able to discover <strong>them all</strong> ?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/17986e5975d758c0afcaafd24d62ad3c.webp?t=1720811359\" width=574 height=44 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/9a42c79e11a2368c6da4776ac731050f.poster.avif?t=1720811359\" width=728 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529190/extras/9a42c79e11a2368c6da4776ac731050f.webm?t=1720811359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The game mechanics reward <u>quick players</u>.<br>Remaining countdown time is converted into <strong>coins</strong>, which can be used to purchase <u>power-ups</u> and <u>landmark blueprints</u>.",
